[
{ type: install
  message: <<EOM
Remember to run:

sysrc puppetserver_enable=yes

OpenVox Server ships with a version of JRuby that bundle an older version of
the json gem than the one provided by the ports pollection.  If
devel/rubygem-json is installed, OpenVox Server may fail to start because it
loads the newer gem version, which lacks Java support.

This can be fixed by running:

puppetserver gem install json
EOM
}
]
